king%20and%20interested%20in%20a%20highly%20competitive%20auto%20marketplace%2C%26quot%3B%20Jim%20Heininger%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20principal%20of%20Chicago%20rebranding%20firm%20The%20Rebranding%20Experts%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20after%20seeing%20the%20conceptual%20car%20rollout.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20masterclass%20in%20what%20rebranding%20can%20accomplish%20for%20a%20company%20%E2%80%94%20a%20new%20forward-facing%20product%20and%20brand%2C%20clearly%20designed%20for%20its%20new%20customer%20persona%2C%20that%20everyone%20is%20talking%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeininger%20%E2%80%94%20whose%2030-year%20career%20includes%20work%20for%20P%26amp%3BG%2C%20McDonald's%2C%20and%20Anheuser-Busch%20%E2%80%94%20argued%20that%20Jaguar%20set%20high%20expectations%20when%20it%20debuted%20its%20controversial%20rebrand%20last%20month.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20concept%20car%20unveiling%20delivered%20on%20those%20expectations.%20The%20car%20effectively%20signals%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bboldly%20modernistic%26quot%3B%20vision%20and%20%26quot%3Bdeparture%20from%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20colors%2C%20design%20shapes%2C%20and%20new%20logo%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20right%20when%20you%20see%20it%20on%20the%20concept%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20concept%20vision%20for%20a%20new%20pink%20Jaguar%20car%20seen%20from%20the%20front.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674e28b67929f317fb4fa1f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20front%20view%20of%20Jaguar's%20concept%20car.%3Cp%3EJaguar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Andersen%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Omaha%2C%20Nebraska%2C%20creative%20agency%20Bailey%20Lauerman%2C%20also%20lauded%20Jag's%20marketing%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20exceeds%20expectations%20is%20the%20breadth%20and%20depth%20of%20the%20Jaguar%20brand%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anderson%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20brands%20such%20as%20Google%2C%20Levi's%2C%20Burberry%2C%20and%20Axe%20before%20joining%20Bailey%20Lauerman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20revealed%20much%20more%20than%20a%20concept%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20it%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20story%20of%20the%20Jaguar%20brand%20vision%2C%20which%20they%20can%20easily%20chapter%20out%20and%20stretch%20to%20the%20production%20model%20reveal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20looking%20to%20the%20future%2C%20Andersen%20said%20the%20company's%20strategy%20has%20to%20remain%20well-executed%20when%20it%20comes%20time%20to%20reveal%20its%20new%20EV%2C%20which%20the%20company%20has%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20happen%20in%20late%202025%20before%20hitting%20showrooms%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20biggest%20risk%20for%20them%20now%20is%20making%20sure%20the%20production%20model%20lives%20up%20to%20the%20promise%20and%20doesn't%20suffer%20death%20by%20a%20thousand%20cuts%2C%26quot%3B%20Andersen%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BRolling%20out%20an%20unapologetic%2C%20future-facing%20brand%20along%20with%20a%20marginally%20better%20car%20might%20not%20go%20so%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bf4107e-b8c8-45d5-9f22-8038e795be62%5C%22%3EThe%20proof%20of%20success%20will%20be%20in%20the%20production%20model%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20not%20all%20of%20the%20ad%20veterans%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20had%20so%20much%20praise%20for%20Jaguar%20and%20its%20rebranding%20rollout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristos%20Joannides%2C%20founder%20and%20creative%20director%20of%20luxury%20branding%20agency%20Flat%206%20Concepts%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Jaguar's%20initial%20rebranding%20announcement%20did%20too%20much%20all%20at%20once%2C%20%26quot%3Boverwhelming%20and%20confusing%26quot%3B%20the%20carmaker's%20long-standing%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20releasing%20its%20concept%20car%20this%20week%2C%20Jaguar%20didn't%20do%20enough%20to%20ground%20its%20new%20ethos%20in%20reality%2C%20Joannides%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoannides%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20Jaguar%20competitors%20like%20Maserati%20and%20Lotus%20%E2%80%94%20argued%20that%20the%20concept%20car's%20features%2C%20like%20the%20rear%20with%20no%20window%20and%20the%20brass-toned%20divider%20running%20through%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20cabin%2C%20are%20impractical%20and%20bizarre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22vision%20concept%20car%20interior%20brass%20lines%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674e2b9de45a68623a2779d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22866%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThree%20brass%20lines%20run%20through%20the%20length%20of%20the%20concept%20car%2C%20with%20one%20right%20down%20the%20middle.%3Cp%3EJaguar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20showcasing%20a%20production%20model%20with%20more%20realistic%20features%2C%20Jaguar%20could%20have%20conveyed%20its%20vision%20more%20effectively%20and%20provided%20tangible%20evidence%20of%20its%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Joannides%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20it%20stands%2C%20the%20concept%20car%20feels%20superficial%20and%20gimmicky%2C%20like%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20be%20different%20without%20any%20real%20substance%20or%20coherent%20strategy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoannides%20said%20that%20while%20Jaguar's%20initial%20teaser%20video%20was%20%26quot%3Bcertainly%20audacious%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20final%20product%20will%20be%20what%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cde8a390-44b1-4ed3-827c-2a5cb87f2e47%5C%22%3EJaguar's%20next%20steps%20in%20its%20rebranding%20rollout%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20which%20specific%20design%20elements%20of%20the%20new%20concept%20will%20be%20implemented%20in%20Jaguar's%20forthcoming%20electric%20vehicle%20models.%20Jaguar%20said%20its%20concept%20car%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20indicator%20of%20design%20philosophy%20and%20intent%20for%20the%20coming%20new%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20available%20for%20purchase%20sometime%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20EV%20model%20will%20use%20dedicated%20Jaguar%20Electric%20Architecture%2C%20have%20a%20projected%20driving%20range%20of%20up%20to%20430%20miles%20on%20a%20single%20charge%2C%20and%20be%20able%20to%20add%20up%20to%20200%20miles%20of%20range%20after%2015%20minutes%20of%20rapid%20charging%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20new%20EVs%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20much%20more%20upscale%20than%20previous%20Jags.%20Though%20Jaguar%20has%20not%20confirmed%20a%20price%20range%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fjaguar-finally-reveals-its-all-electric-type-00%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWired%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20without%20citing%20a%20source%2C%20that%20the%20new%20Jag%20could%20likely%20cost%20at%20least%20%24127%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20a%20significant%20increase%20from%20current%20average%20prices%20of%20around%20%2470%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20forged%20a%20fearlessly%20creative%20new%20character%20for%20Jaguar%20that%20is%20true%20to%20the%20DNA%20of%20the%20brand%20but%20future-facing%2C%20relevant%2C%20and%20one%20that%20really%20stands%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaguar%20managing%20director%20Rawdon%20Glover%20said%20of%20Monday's%20concept%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjaguar-strategy-new-model-rebranding-reviewed-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733358076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6750cd5bef9a5d904789f9d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjaguar-strategy-new-model-rebranding-reviewed-2024-