%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20forces%20in%20Gaza%20have%20deployed%20quadcopter%20drones%2C%20playing%20the%20sounds%20of%20crying%20babies%20and%20distressed%20women%2C%20to%20draw%20Palestinians%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20in%20open%20areas%20where%20they%20can%20be%20targeted.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20mid-April%2C%20we%20were%20informed%20that%20Israeli%20quadcopters%20were%20emitting%20bizarre%20sounds%2C%20including%20baby%20sounds%20or%20women%20screaming%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maha%20Hussaini%2C%20Euro-Med%20Human%20Rights%20monitor%2C%20told%20Al%20Jazeera.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CI%20went%20personally%20to%20Nuseirat%20and%20I%20interviewed%20several%20Palestinians%20separately%20and%20the%20testimonies%20were%20almost%20identical%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20drones%20were%20%E2%80%9Cplaying%20sounds%20of%20screaming%20women%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Clure%20citizens%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20to%20find%20someone%20to%20shoot%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20This%20was%20confirmed%20by%20the%20hospital%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BQuadcopters%20were%20emitting%20baby%20sounds%2C%20playing%20sounds%20of%20screaming%20women.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPalestinians%20in%20Gaza%20say%20Israel%20has%20been%20using%20small%20quadcopter%20drones%2C%20equipped%20with%20loudspeakers%2C%20to%20lure%20them%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20then%20shoot%20them.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGazaCrimes%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23GazaCrimes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FW4VytzyvdA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FW4VytzyvdA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Al%20Jazeera%20Investigations%20(%40AJIunit)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAJIunit%2Fstatus%2F1863553707897680291%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20cases%20of%20people%20getting%20injured%20by%20these%20quad%20captors%20after%20going%20out%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20was%20the%20sound%20to%20try%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNuseirat%20resident%20Mohammad%20Nabhan%20recalled%20hearing%20a%20woman%20shouting%20%E2%80%9Chelp%E2%80%9D%20alongside%20the%20cries%20of%20a%20baby.%20On%20realising%20that%20the%20sounds%20emanated%20from%20a%20quadcopter%2C%20Mr%20Nabhan%20warned%20his%20cousin%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon't%20fall%20for%20it%3B%20it's%20a%20sound%20system.%E2%80%9D%20Abu%20Anas%20Al-Shahrour%2C%20a%20neighbour%2C%20heard%20the%20cries%20of%20distress%20and%20went%20out%20to%20help%20but%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20head.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOther%20incidents%20across%20Gaza%2C%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20and%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20included%20recordings%20of%20a%20child%20crying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20my%20mother%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20threats%20warning%20Palestinians%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20die%E2%80%9D%20if%20they%20resist.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnQuadcopters%2C%20remote-controlled%20drones%2C%20have%20been%20extensively%20used%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20since%20the%20escalation%20of%20hostilities%20on%20October%207.%20These%20devices%20have%20been%20utilised%20for%20surveillance%2C%20individual%20targeting%2C%20and%20crowd%20dispersal.%20In%20January%2C%20witnesses%20reported%20quadcopters%20opening%20fire%20on%20hundreds%20of%20civilians%20who%20had%20gathered%20to%20collect%20food%20on%20al-Rasheed%20Street%20in%20Gaza%20City.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20drones'%20sound%20systems%20have%20also%20broadcast%20Hebrew%20and%20Arabic%20songs%2C%20sounds%20of%20tank%20movements%2C%20and%20even%20the%20familiar%20calls%20of%20local%20vendors.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Health%20Ministry%20in%20Gaza%20has%20reported%20nearly%2045%2C000%20deaths%20and%20the%20entire%20population%20has%20been%20displaced%20amid%20relentless%20Israeli%20bombardment.%20Civilians%20are%20facing%20acute%20shortages%20of%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20medical%20supplies.%20Hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20homes%20lie%20in%20ruins%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20spread%20of%20disease%20in%20overcrowded%20shelters%20looms%20large.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20method%20of%20psychological%20warfare%20has%20drawn%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20human%20rights%20groups.%20The%20%26quot%3BGeneral's%20Plan%26quot%3B%2C%20allegedly%20aiming%20to%20depopulate%20northern%20Gaza%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20fighting%20Hamas%2C%20has%20been%20labelled%20a%20war%20crime%20by%20the%20ICC%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20issuance%20of%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733336160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F8rhc66g_gaza-reuters_625x300_01_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraeli-quadcopters-emit-baby-cries-and-screams-of-women-to-lure-out-palestinians-in-gaza-7169067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20forces%20in%20Gaza%20have%20deployed%20quadcopter%20drones%2C%20playing%20the%20sounds%20of%20crying%20babies%20and%20distressed%20women%2C%20to%20draw%20Palestinians%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20in%20open%20areas%20where%20they%20can%20be%20targeted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShould%20I%20Call%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Man%20Illegally%20Enters%20Salman%20Khan's%20Set%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20illegally%20entered%20a%20location%20where%20Salman%20Khan%20was%20shooting%20for%20a%20film%20in%20Mumbai%20and%2C%20when%20questioned%2C%20asked%20whether%20he%20should%20call%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20police%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20Mr%20Khan%20was%20shooting%20for%20a%20film%20in%20Dadar's%20Shivaji%20Park%20area%20on%20Wednesday%20when%20the%20man%20entered%20the%20venue.%20Finding%20his%20movements%20suspicious%2C%20some%20people%20asked%20him%20what%20he%20was%20doing%2C%20only%20for%20the%20man%20to%20respond%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EBishnoi%20ko%20bulau%20kya%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Should%20I%20call%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%3F)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20the%20Shivaji%20Park%20police%20station%2C%20where%20he%20is%20being%20questioned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bishnoi%20gang%20had%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20shooting%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20house%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20in%20April.%20The%20actor's%20name%20had%20also%20come%20up%20when%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20said%20it%20had%20killed%20former%20Maharashtra%20minister%20Baba%20Siddique%20in%20Bandra%20in%20October.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20gang%20had%20allegedly%20said%20that%20the%20politician%20was%20close%20to%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20that%20anyone%20who%20helped%20the%20actor%20would%20also%20be%20in%20its%20crosshairs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20has%20been%20receiving%20a%20string%20of%20threats%2C%20especially%20since%20Baba%20Siddique's%20killing%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20have%20also%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20fake.%20Last%20month%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20lyricist%20of%20a%20song%20in%20an%20upcoming%20Salman%20Khan%20was%20arrested%20for%20sending%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20actor%20and%20himself%2C%20purportedly%20from%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang.%20Police%20had%20said%20the%20lyricist%20had%20called%20the%20Mumbai%20traffic%20control%20room%20and%20issued%20the%20threat%20because%20he%20wanted%20the%20song%2C%20which%20mentions%20Bishnoi%2C%20to%20get%20publicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20another%20person%20had%20called%20up%20the%20Mumbai%20police%20control%20room%20and%20threatened%20that%20the%20actor%20would%20be%20killed%20unless%20he%20paid%20Rs%202%20crore%20as%20ransom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Salman%20Khan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20which%20became%20a%20household%20name%20after%20claiming%20responsibility%20for%20murdering%20musician%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20in%202022%2C%20has%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20kill%20Salman%20Khan%20because%20of%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20shooting%20blackbucks%20at%20Bawad%20in%20Mathania%20near%20Jodhpur%20in%20September%201998%2C%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20'Hum%20Saath%20Saath%20Hain'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20act%20had%20upset%20the%20Bishnoi%20community%2C%20which%20considers%20the%20blackbuck%20sacred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%20had%20also%20said%20during%20a%20court%20appearance%20in%202018%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20kill%20Salman%20Khan%20in%20Jodhpur.%20Everyone%20will%20know%20once%20we%20take%20action.%20I%20have%20not%20done%20anything%20as%20of%20now%2C%20they%20are%20accusing%20me%20of%20crimes%20for%20no%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733336160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F18pl1k8g_salman-khan-lawrence-bishnoi_625x300_08_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-breaches-salman-khans-shooting-venue-takes-gangster-lawrence-bishnois-name-7173601%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20illegally%20entered%20a%20location%20where%20Salman%20Khan%20was%20shooting%20for%20a%20film%20in%20Mumbai%20and%2C%20when%20questioned%2C%20asked%20whether%20he%20should%20call%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20police%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-breaches-salman-khans-shooting-venue-takes-gangster-lawrence-bishnois-name-7173601%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wife%20of%20slain%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20r