r%20Cracked%3B%20Killer%20Was%20Son%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECracking%20the%20case%20of%20the%20grisly%20murder%20of%20a%20couple%20and%20their%2023-year-old%20daughter%20in%20South%20Delhi's%20Neb%20Sarai%20in%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20the%20police%20have%20said%20that%20the%20killings%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20couple's%20son%2C%20who%20had%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20on%20a%20morning%20walk%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20had%20not%20only%20alerted%20the%20police%20about%20the%20murders%20but%20also%20allegedly%20called%20up%20his%20uncle%20and%20informed%20him.%20Officials%20said%20he%20had%20stabbed%20his%20family%20to%20death%20in%20their%20sleep%20because%20he%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bhumiliated%26quot%3B%20by%20his%20father%20and%20had%20found%20out%20that%20his%20parents%20intended%20to%20leave%20their%20property%20to%20his%20sister.%20The%20police%20said%20he%20had%20been%20planning%20the%20murders%20for%20a%20while%20and%20had%20decided%20to%20carry%20them%20out%20on%20his%20parents'%20wedding%20anniversary.%20He%20has%20now%20been%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20of%20Rajesh%20Kumar%2C%2051%2C%20his%20wife%20Komal%2C%2046%2C%20and%20their%2023-year-old%20daughter%20Kavita%20were%20found%20in%20their%20house%20in%20Neb%20Sarai%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%20Rajesh%20and%20Komal's%20son%2C%20Arjun%2C%2020%2C%20had%20claimed%20he%20had%20left%20for%20his%20morning%20walk%20around%205.30%20am%20and%20found%20the%20bodies%20when%20he%20had%20returned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20celebrating%20their%2027th%20wedding%20anniversary%20and%20neighbours%20who%20had%20seen%20the%20bodies%20had%20said%20that%20Rajesh%2C%20Komal%20and%20Kavita%20were%20stabbed%20in%20the%20throat.%20A%20neighbour%20said%20Arjun%20had%20told%20them%20he%20had%20left%20for%20the%20walk%20after%20wishing%20his%20parents%20a%20happy%20anniversary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20bodies%20were%20recovered%2C%20the%20police%20checked%20footage%20from%20CCTV%20cameras%2C%20which%20convinced%20them%20that%20no%20one%20from%20outside%20the%20family%20had%20entered%20the%20house%2C%20Joint%20Commissioner%20Of%20Police%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Jain%20said.%20There%20were%20also%20no%20signs%20of%20forced%20entry%20into%20the%20house%20and%20nothing%20was%20stolen%20or%20ransacked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20said%20that%2C%20on%20further%20investigation%2C%20Arjun's%20version%20seemed%20suspicious%20as%20there%20were%20many%20contradictions%20in%20his%20statements.%20He%20said%20Arjun%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20and%20confessed%20to%20the%20murders%20after%20%26quot%3Bsustained%20examination%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjun%20did%20his%20schooling%20at%20Army%20Public%20School%2C%20Dhaula%20Kuan%20and%20is%20a%20second-year%20Bachelor%20of%20Arts%20student%20at%20Delhi%20University.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20trained%20boxer%20and%20represented%20Delhi%20in%20a%20boxing%20event%2C%20where%20he%20won%20a%20silver%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20said%20Arjun%20told%20the%20police%20that%20his%20father%2C%20Rajesh%2C%20was%20an%20ex-serviceman%20and%20scolded%20him%20regularly%20about%20academics%20and%20chores.%20Rajesh%2C%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20had%20also%20shouted%20at%20and%20thrashed%20Arjun%20and%20%26quot%3Bhumiliated%26quot%3B%20him%20in%20front%20of%20his%20neighbours%20recently.%20Arjun%20also%20felt%20no%20one%20supported%20him%20in%20the%20family%2C%20which%20had%20led%20him%20to%20harbour%20a%20grudge%20against%20his%20parents%20and%20sister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjun%20also%20felt%20neglected%20and%20isolated%2C%20Mr%20Jain%20said%2C%20and%20flew%20into%20a%20rage%20when%20he%20found%20out%20that%20his%20father%20wanted%20to%20leave%20his%20property%20to%20his%20sister%20in%20his%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20premeditated%20the%20plan%20to%20eliminate%20his%20family%20members.%20He%20chose%20December%204%20since%20it%20was%20the%20marriage%20anniversary%20of%20his%20parents.%20To%20create%20a%20web%20of%20deception%2C%20he%20went%20out%20at%205.30%20am%20to%20have%20an%20alibi%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Unimaginable'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%2C%20originally%20from%20Haryana%2C%20had%20moved%20to%20Delhi%2015%20years%20ago%20to%20ensure%20better%20academic%20and%20career%20opportunities%20for%20the%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20horrific%20incident.%20Yesterday%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20mother%20and%20daughter%20on%20their%20terrace%2C%20talking%20and%20laughing.%20Today%2C%20they're%20no%20longer%20alive.%20Crime%20has%20become%20so%20common%2C%20but%20experiencing%20it%20first-hand%20has%20completely%20shaken%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Himani%2C%20a%20neighbour%2C%C2%A0was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mother-daughter%20duo%20were%20approachable%20and%20kind%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20colony.%20It's%20unimaginable%20that%20something%20so%20tragic%20could%20happen%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20neighbour%2C%20Anjali%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP%20Attacks%20Centre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20murder%20was%20cracked%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20had%20attacked%20the%20Centre%2C%20which%20controls%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20failing%20to%20ensure%20the%20security%20of%20residents%20in%20the%20National%20Capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20triple%20murder%20in%20Neb%20Sarai%20this%20morning.%20Murders%20are%20happening%20in%20broad%20daylight%20in%20Delhi%2C%20bullets%20are%20being%20fired%2C%20and%20drugs%20are%20being%20sold%20openly.%20The%20central%20government%20has%20only%20one%20responsibility%20in%20Delhi%20-%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20They%20have%20completely%20failed%20in%20their%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20and%20AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20had%20liquid%20thrown%20on%20him%20-%20a%20serious%20breach%20of%20security%20-%20during%20a%20'%3Cem%3Epadyatra'%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Delhi%20on%20November%2030%2C%20%C2%A0also%20lost%20no%20time%20in%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20murders%20in%20the%20same%20house%20in%20Neb%20Sarai...%20This%20is%20extremely%20painful%20and%20frightening.%20Every%20day%2C%20Delhiites%20wake%20up%20to%20such%20frightening%20news.%20Criminals%20have%20been%20given%20a%20free%20hand%2C%20and%20law%20and%20order%20has%20collapsed.%20Homes%20are%20being%20destroyed%2C%20innocent%20lives%20are%20being%20lost.%20And%20those%20who%20are%20responsible%20are%20silently%20watching%20all%20this%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733331180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fpablekg_delhi-neb-sarai-killer-arjun_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-murders-neb-sarai-south-delhi-delhir-murder-son-killed-delhi-parents-sister-on-wedding-anniversary-went-for-walk-cops-7173141%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cracking%20the%20case%20of%20the%20grisly%20murder%20of%20a%20couple%20and%20their%2023-year-old%20daughter%20in%20South%20Delhi's%20Neb%20Sarai%20in%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20the%20police%20have%20said%20that%20the%20killings%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20couple's%20son%2C%20who%20had%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20on%20a%20morning%20walk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20France's%20turmoil%20is%20grave%20concern%20for%20Europe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe