ificant%20agreement%20was%20signed%20in%20Beijing%20today%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20China%20to%20make%20major%20inroads%20in%20Nepal.%20Seven%20years%20after%20an%20initial%20understanding%20for%20Kathmandu%20to%20be%20part%20of%20Beijing's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20or%20BRI%2C%20today's%20agreement%20lays%20the%20framework%20of%20how%20projects%20will%20be%20executed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20tradition%20of%20making%20New%20Delhi%20a%20Nepalese%20prime%20minister's%20first%20port%20of%20call%20after%20election%20results%2C%20KP%20Sharma%20Oli%20chose%20to%20visit%20Beijing%20instead.%20He%20has%20been%20in%20China%20since%20Monday%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20finalise%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F4bccifok_nepal-china-bilateral-talks_625x300_04_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20and%20Nepal%20have%20%26quot%3Bsigned%20the%20framework%20for%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Cooperation%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Nepal's%20foreign%20office%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20today%2C%20but%20shared%20no%20further%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20familiar%20with%20the%20agreement%20have%20said%20that%20today's%20deal%20means%20both%20countries%20will%20not%20plan%20and%20coordinate%20the%20details%20of%20each%20project.%20It%20also%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20China%20to%20fund%20these%20projects%20and%20how%20exactly%20each%20project%20would%20be%20financed%20by%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20align%3D%5C%22center%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Government%20of%20Nepal%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20People's%20Republic%20of%20China%20signed%20the%20Framework%20for%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Cooperation%20today.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6oTlDvTzIe%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6oTlDvTzIe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20MOFA%20of%20Nepal%20%F0%9F%87%B3%F0%9F%87%B5%20(%40MofaNepal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMofaNepal%2Fstatus%2F1864210839940812810%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Nepal%20had%20agreed%20in-principle%20to%20be%20part%20of%20China's%20mega%20Belt%20and%20Road%20project%20-%20a%20massive%20network%20of%20roads%2C%20transport%20corridors%2C%20airports%2C%20and%20rail%20lines%20connecting%20China%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20Asia%2C%20Europe%20and%20beyond.%20However%2C%20no%20progress%20was%20made%20in%20the%20last%20seven%20years%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20proper%20framework%20of%20executing%20them.%20Kathmandu%20also%20struggled%20to%20find%20political%20consensus%20on%20the%20issue.%20That%20now%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20addressed%20with%20today's%20pact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%2C%20though%20ambitious%2C%20has%20been%20a%20red%20flag%20for%20many%20countries%20due%20to%20Beijing's%20suspicious%20dealings%20and%20ulterior%20motives.%20Several%20countries%20have%20fallen%20in%20a%20debt%20trap%2C%20often%20called%20China's%20%26quot%3Bdebt%20diplomacy%26quot%3B%20wherein%20China%20builds%20a%20mega%20project%20on%20credit%20in%20a%20smaller%20country%20in%20terms%20of%20economy%2C%20and%20when%20the%20country%20cannot%20pay%20back%20the%20loan%20or%20interest%2C%20Beijing%20either%20takes%20over%20the%20project%20for%20a%20lifetime%20or%20cuts%20a%20deal%20to%20forward%20its%20expansionist%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20has%20also%20had%20a%20history%20of%20ignoring%20the%20national%20security%20concerns%20and%20violating%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20other%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20leaders%20in%20Nepal's%20government%20and%20opposition%20are%20concerned%20over%20debt%20concerns%20mounting%20in%20an%20already-stretched%20economy.%20Even%20within%20Prime%20Minister%20Oli's%20government%2C%20there%20is%20fierce%20debate%20over%20the%20potential%20risks%20in%20mega%20projects%20executed%20by%20China.%20Nepal%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20a%20key%20ally%20of%20PM%20Oli's%20party%2C%20has%20vehemently%20opposed%20any%20projects%20funded%20by%20Chinese%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20had%20funded%20the%20airport%20project%20in%20Pokhra%20-%20Nepal's%20second-largest%20city%20-%20by%20loaning%20more%20than%20%24200%20million.%20Nepal%20went%20ahead%20with%20the%20project%20despite%20India%20raising%20serious%20concerns%20and%20opened%20the%20airport%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20airport%20has%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20losses%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20international%20flights.%20This%20can%20partially%20be%20due%20to%20a%20slender%20demand%20for%20airlines%2C%20but%20also%20due%20to%20India's%20refusal%20to%20planes%20using%20its%20airspace%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPokhra%2C%20located%20around%20120%20kilometers%20from%20Kathmandu%2C%20is%20less%20than%2020%20minutes%20from%20the%20India%20border%20by%20commercial%20flight.%20India%20had%20to%20shut%20its%20airspace%20out%20of%20a%20national%20security%20compulsion%20because%20Kathmandu%20ignored%20New%20Delhi's%20concerns%20that%20China%20may%20use%20the%20airport%20to%20station%20its%20military%20aircraft%20and%20helicopters%20-%20a%20massive%20national%20security%20threat%20for%20New%20Delhi.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733329980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F3avksduc_nepal-pm-kp-sharma-oli-meets-xi-jinping-twitter_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnepal-joins-chinas-belt-and-road-initiative-raises-concerns-for-new-delhi-7173147%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20significant%20agreement%20wa