20task%20while%20hearing%20a%20case%20about%20woman%20judges%20sacked%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20While%20it%20was%20alleged%20that%20all%20showed%20poor%20performance%2C%20one%20of%20them%20was%20pregnant%20and%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage%20in%20the%20period%20in%20which%20she%20was%20judged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20such%20criteria%20is%20also%20imposed%20on%20male%20judges.%20I%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20saying%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%2C%20pulling%20up%20the%20High%20Court%20for%20its%20apathy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lady%2C%20she%20has%20got%20pregnant%20and%20she%20had%20miscarriage.%20The%20mental%20and%20physical%20trauma%20of%20a%20lady%20who%20has%20undergone%20a%20miscarriage.%20What%20is%20this%3F%20I%20wish%20men%20have%20menstruation.%20Then%20they%20will%20know%20what%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Justice%20Nagarathna%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20two-judge%20bench%20that%20heard%20the%20matter%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20taken%20up%20the%20matter%20on%20its%20own%20in%20November%20last%20year%20and%20sought%20clarification%20from%20the%20high%20court%20on%20the%20criteria%20for%20the%20termination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20termination%20orders%20for%20the%20women%20judges%2C%20who%20were%20on%20probation%2C%20were%20passed%20in%20June%202023%20by%20the%20state%20law%20department%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20high%20court.%20The%20performance%20rating%20had%20taken%20into%20account%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20they%20had%20disposed%20of.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20August%2C%20a%20full%20court%20had%20a%20rethink%20and%20decided%20to%20reinstate%20four%20of%20the%20judges.%20But%20Aditi%20Kumar%20Sharma%20was%20not%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20report%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said%20her%20performance%20dropped%20from%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20ratings%20during%202019-20%20to%20%26quot%3Baverage%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20subsequent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20she%20was%20on%20maternity%20and%20child%20care%20leave%20when%20she%20had%20her%20miscarriage%2C%20Ms%20Sharma%2C%20in%20her%20note%20to%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20said%20counting%20it%20as%20part%20of%20her%20performance%20would%20be%20a%20grave%20injustice.%20Also%2C%20the%20termination%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20her%20fundamental%20right%20to%20equality%20and%20right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20settled%20law%20that%20maternity%20and%20child%20care%20leave%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%20of%20a%20woman%20and%20also%20the%20infant%2C%20therefore%2C%20evaluation%20of%20the%20applicant's%20performance%20for%20the%20probation%20period%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20leave%20taken%20by%20her%20as%20part%20of%20maternity%20and%20child%20care%20is%20grossly%20violative%20of%20her%20fundamental%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20petition%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20had%20also%20argued%20that%20she%20was%20sacked%20without%20following%20any%20due%20process%20of%20law%20despite%20four%20years%20of%20unblemished%20service%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733328480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fs17p8ubo_supreme-court_625x300_03_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwish-men-menstruated-top-court-on-woman-judge-sacked-after-miscarriage-7172965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20to%20task%20while%20hearing%20a%20case%20about%20woman%20judges%20sacked%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20While%20it%20was%20alleged%20that%20all%20showed%20poor%20performance%2C%20one%20of%20them%20was%20pregnant%20and%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage%20in%20the%20peri%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%2