st%20like%20their%20father%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMujibur%20Rahman%20was%20assassinated%20in%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20first%20public%20address%20after%20taking%20shelter%20in%20India%20following%20her%20resignation%20in%20August%20in%20the%20face%20of%20massive%20anti-government%20protests%2C%20though%20she%20had%20commented%20on%20the%20overall%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20armed%20protestors%20were%20directed%20towards%20Ganabhaban.%20If%20the%20security%20guards%20opened%20fire%2C%20many%20lives%20would%20have%20been%20lost.%20It%20was%20a%20matter%20of%2025-30%20minutes%2C%20and%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20leave.%20I%20told%20them%20%5Bguards%5D%20not%20to%20fire%20no%20matter%20what%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20referring%20to%20the%20storming%20of%20her%20official%20residence%20in%20Dhaka%20on%20August%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20I%20am%20being%20accused%20of%20genocide.%20In%20reality%2C%20Yunus%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20genocide%20in%20a%20meticulously%20designed%20manner.%20The%20masterminds%20--%20the%20student%20coordinators%20and%20Yunus%20--%20are%20behind%20this%20genocide%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20the%20event%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20said%20the%20current%20ruling%20dispensation%20in%20Dhaka%20failed%20to%20protect%20the%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindus%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Christians%20--%20no%20one%20has%20been%20spared.%20Eleven%20churches%20have%20been%20razed%2C%20temples%20and%20Buddhist%20shrines%20have%20been%20broken.%20When%20the%20Hindus%20protested%2C%20the%20Iskcon%20leader%20was%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20an%20oblique%20reference%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20Hindu%20monk%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20this%20persecution%20of%20minorities%20for%3F%20Why%20are%20they%20being%20ruthlessly%20persecuted%20and%20attacked%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20no%20longer%20have%20the%20right%20to%20justice...%20I%20never%20even%20got%20the%20time%20to%20resign%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20speaking%20in%20Bengali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20said%20she%20left%20Bangladesh%20in%20August%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%2C%20but%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20came%20under%20strain%20after%20the%20interim%20government%20headed%20by%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20came%20to%20power.%20India%20has%20been%20expressing%20concerns%20over%20attacks%20on%20minorities%2C%20especially%20Hindus%2C%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20has%20been%20staying%20in%20India%20since%20she%20left%20Bangladesh%20following%20massive%20anti-government%20protests%20in%20July%20and%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20speech%20at%20the%20event%20hosted%20to%20mark%20Bangladesh's%20'Vijay%20Diwas'%2C%20the%20Awami%20League%20leader%20also%20alleged%20that%20there%20was%20a%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20were%20dying%20indiscriminately%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20should%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20spate%20of%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20including%20on%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20last%20week%20said%20the%20interim%20government%20in%20Bangladesh%20must%20live%20up%20to%20its%20responsibility%20of%20protecting%20all%20minorities%20as%20it%20expressed%20serious%20concern%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bsurge%26quot%3B%20of%20extremist%20rhetoric%20and%20increasing%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20also%20hoped%20that%20the%20case%20relating%20to%20Das%2C%20arrested%20on%20a%20charge%20of%20sedition%2C%20would%20be%20dealt%20with%20in%20a%20just%2C%20fair%20and%20transparent%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20position%20on%20the%20matter%20is%20very%20clear%20--%20the%20interim%20government%20must%20live%20up%20to%20its%20responsibility%20of%20protecting%20all%20minorities%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20at%20his%20weekly%20media%20briefing%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20concerned%20at%20the%20surge%20of%20extremist%20rhetoric%2C%20increasing%20incidents%20of%20violence%20and%20provocation.%20These%20developments%20cannot%20be%20dismissed%20only%20as%20media%20exaggeration.%20We%20once%20again%20call%20upon%20Bangladesh%20to%20take%20all%20steps%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20minorities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733326860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fpp02ivl_sheikh-hasina-ians_625x300_28_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmuhammad-yunus-involved-in-genocide-sheikh-hasina-in-1st-public-address-7172709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ousted%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20has%20mounted%20a%20stinging%20attack%20on%20the%20country's%20interim%20leader%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20over%20alleged%20persecution%20of%20minorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmuhammad-yunus-involved-in-genocide-sheikh-hasina-in-1st-public-address-7172709%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rise%20in%20DIY%20investing%3A%20Direct%20plans%20now%20make%20up%20around%2040%25%20of%20SIPs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733326825000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fmutual-fun