%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20a%20statewide%20ban%20on%20serving%20and%20consumption%20of%20beef%20in%20restaurants%2C%20hotels%20and%20public%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20state%20cabinet%20meeting%20to%20amend%20the%20existing%20law%20on%20beef%20consumption%20to%20incorporate%20the%20new%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumption%20of%20beef%20is%20not%20illegal%20in%20Assam%2C%20but%20The%20Assam%20Cattle%20Preservation%20Act%20of%202021%20regulates%20the%20transportation%2C%20and%20slaughter%20of%20all%20cattle%2C%20and%20sale%20of%20beef%20and%20beef%20products%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20earlier%20introduced%20a%20bill%20in%20Assam%20to%20protect%20cows%20and%20we%20have%20been%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20legislation%20that%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20state%20assembly%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20further%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20that%20beef%20will%20not%20be%20served%20in%20any%20hotels%20or%20restaurants%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20will%20also%20not%20be%20served%20during%20any%20public%20function%20or%20in%20any%20public%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Cattle%20Preservation%20Act%20of%202021%20bans%20cattle%20slaughter%20and%20sale%20of%20beef%20in%20areas%20where%20Hindus%2C%20Jains%20and%20Sikhs%20are%20in%20majority%20and%20within%20a%20five%20kilometre%20radius%20of%20a%20temple%20or%20satra%20(Vaishnavite%20monastery).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20we%20had%20decided%20to%20place%20the%20curbs%20within%20a%20five%20kilometre%20radius%20of%20a%20temple%20but%20now%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20expand%20it%20to%20other%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20All%20India%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(AIUDF)%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20state%20government%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20diverting%20attention%20from%20key%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20carry%20out%20development%20works...%20it%20has%20failed%20to%20tackle%20unemployment.%20There%20are%20major%20issues%20in%20the%20education%20and%20health%20sector...%20they%20are%20simply%20diverting%20the%20people's%20attention%20through%20such%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20AIUDF%20legislator%20Aminul%20Islam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Cattle%20Preservation%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Assam%20Assembly%20through%20a%20voice%20vote%20in%20August%202021%2C%20amid%20a%20walkout%20from%20the%20Opposition%2C%20who%20wanted%20the%20legislation%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20Select%20Committee%20for%20a%20detailed%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolations%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20bill%20could%20lead%20to%20imprisonment%20for%20three%20to%20eight%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20between%20%E2%82%B93%20lakh%20and%20%E2%82%B95%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733325720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Flvnebul8_himanta-biswa-sarma_625x300_28_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-bans-consumption-of-beef-in-hotels-public-places-7172358%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20a%20statewide%20ban%20on%20serving%20and%20consumption%20of%20beef%20in%20restaurants%2C%20hotels%20and%20public%20places.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-bans-consumption-of-beef-in-hotels-public-places-7172358%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boss%20of%20healthcare%20giant%20shot%20dead%20'by%20gunman%20with%20silencer%20dressed%20in%20black'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733325120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F12%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-brian-thompson-unitedhealthcare_6766533.jpg%3F20241204161127%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fus-healthcare-executive-shot-dead-outside-manhattan-hotel-13266807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20executive%20at%20a%20major%20US%20healthcare%20company%20has%20been%20shot%20dead%20in%20New%20York%20in%20what%20was%20reportedly%20a%20targeted%20attack.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A213%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fus-healthcare-executive-shot-dead-outside-manhattan-hotel-13266807%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fus-healthcare-executive-shot-dead-outside-manhattan-hotel-13266807%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fus-healthcare-executive-shot-dead-outside-manhattan-hotel-13266807%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOn%20The%20Face%20Of%20It%2C%20You%20Are%20Corrupt%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20To%20Bengal%20Ex%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20you%20are%20a%20corrupt%20person.%20Crores%20of%20rupees%20were%20recovered%20from%20your%20premises%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20told%20former%20West%20Bengal%20minister%20Partha%20Chatterjee%2C%20arrested%20in%20an%20alleged%20cash-for-job%20scam%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%2C%20which%20reserved%20its%20verdict%20on%20the%20bail%20plea%20of%20Chatterjee%2C%20questioned%20the%20enforcement%20directorate%20(ED)%20over%20his%20continued%20incarceration%20saying%20he%20could%20not%20be%20kept%20inside%20for%20an%20indefinite%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20face%20of%20it%20you%20are%20a%20corrupt%20person.%20Crores%20of%20rupees%20were%20recovered%20from%20your%20premises.%20What%20message%20do%20you%20want%20us%20to%20send%20to%20society%3F%20That%20a%20corrupt%20person%20can%20get%20bail%20like%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20senior%20advocate%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mr%20Chatterjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rohatgi%20said%20except%20for%20his%20client%20all%20other%20co-accused%20persons%20were%20granted%20bail%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20latest%20being%20a%20week%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20everyone%20was%20a%20minister%20Mr%20Rohatgi.%20You%20were%20at%20the%20top.%20You%20can't%20seek%20parity%20with%20others.%20Yes%2C%20you%20can%20question%20the%20delay%20in%20investigation%20and%20role%20of%20prosecution%20but%20not%20the%20merit%20of%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20Mr%20Rohatgi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20ED%20said%20that%20even%20if%20Mr%20Chatterjee%20was%20granted%20bail%20in%20this%20case%2C%20he%20wouldn't%20walk%20out%20of%20jail%20because%20he%20faced%20CBI%20cases%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rohatgi%20objected%20to%20Mr%20Raju's%20statement%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20he%20is%20having%20great%20sadistic%20pleasure.%20Whatever%20happens%20in%20other%20cases%20is%20my%20lookout.%20I%20have%20to%20start%20somewhere.%20What%20kind%20of%20argument%20is%20he%20making%3F%20I%20have%20been%20inside%20for%202.5%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kant%20asked%20Mr%20Raju%20about%20the%20time%20required%20by%20the%20agency%20to%20complete%20the%20investigation%20as%20the%20court%20had%20to%20balance%20the%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rohatgi%20said%20that%20money%20was%20not%20recovered%20from%20his%20client%20but%20from%20the%20premises%20belonging%20to%20a%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20Mr%20Chatterjee%20had%20a%20de-facto%20control%20of%20the%20company%20and%20properties%20were%20purchased%20in%20the%20joint%20name%20of%20his%20and%20one%20Arpita%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20becoming%20minister%2C%20you%20placed%20dummy%20persons.%20Earlier%20you%20controlled%20yourself.%20Cases%20are%20of%202022.%20You%20were%20a%20minister%2C%20obviously%20you%20are%20not%20going%20to%20order%20an%20investigation%20against%20yourself.%20Investigation%20started%20only%20because%20of%20judicial%20intervention.%20Allegation%20is%20that%20Rs%2028%20crore%20was%20recovered.%20Of%20course%20such%20a%20big%20amount%20would%20not%20have%20been%20kept%20in%20residence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20told%20Mr%20Rohatgi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20court%20needed%20to%20examine%20whether%20releasing%20him%20would%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20investigation%20and%20the%20conditions%20to%20be%20imposed%2C%20as%20he%20cannot%20be%20kept%20inside%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rohatgi%20said%20his%20client%20was%20in%20his%20seventies%20and%20had%20collapsed%20even%20during%20court%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20conditions%20can%20be%20imposed%20like%20he%20would%20not%20enter%20the%20area%20or%20he%20would%20live%20somewhere%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20reserved%20its%20order%20after%20hearing%20the%20arguments%20from%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2027%2C%20the%20top%20court%20questioned%20the%20ED%20over%20the%20low%20rate%20of%20convictions%20in%20money%20laundering%20cases%2C%20wondering%20for%20how%20long%20the%20former%20West%20Bengal%20minister%20could%20be%20kept%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20October%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20ED%20on%20the%20appeal%20filed%20by%20Mr%20Chatterjee%20against%20an%20April%2030%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%20denying%20him%20bail%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20was%20established%20against%20him%20under%20the%20PMLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chatterjee%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%2