0oath%20and%20subsequent%20government%20formation.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20had%20reciprocated%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BTwo-and-a-half%20year%20ago%2C%20Fadnavis%20recommended%20my%20name%20to%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20This%20time%2C%20we%20recommend%20his%20name%20to%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20declaring%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bobstacle%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20BJP%20decision%20on%20the%20top%20post%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20had%20gone%20off%20to%20his%20village%20in%20Satara.%20His%20aides%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20had%20kept%20up%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20government%2C%20reiterating%20their%20demand%20for%20the%20top%20post%20for%20their%20boss.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20was%20admitted%20in%20a%20hospital%20for%20what%20his%20team%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Broutine%20check-up%26quot%3B.%20Shortly%20after%20his%20return%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20had%20visited%20him%20in%20%26quot%3BVarsha%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20BJP%20legislators'%20meet%20today%20where%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20was%20named%20as%20chief%2C%20ending%20the%20two-week%20suspense%20that%20had%20drawn%20Opposition%20jeers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20-%20who%20was%20rewarded%20with%20the%20top%20post%20in%202022%20after%20he%20split%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20joined%20forces%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20government%20-%20had%20run%20out%20of%20aces%20this%20time%20after%20the%20BJP's%20massive%20score%20in%20the%20election%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20prompt%20decision%20to%20support%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20for%20the%20top%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20his%20party%20leaders%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Shinde%20government's%20welfare%20schemes%20that%20steered%20the%20Mahayuti%20to%20victory.%20Some%20of%20his%20leaders%20openly%20questioned%20why%2