nk%20he%20(Shah)%20has%20got%20a%20great%20opportunity%20to%20use%20what%20he's%20got%20in%20his%20background%20to%20help%20India%20take%20the%20game%20to%20another%20level%2C%20but%20without%20making%20it%20sort%20of%20under%20the%20yoke%20of%20India%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Barclay%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20'The%20Telegraph'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20really%20lucky%20to%20have%20India%2C%20they're%20a%20massive%20contributor%20to%20the%20game%20across%20all%20the%20measures%2C%20but%20one%20country%20having%20that%20amount%20of%20power%20and%20influence%20does%20distort%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20other%20outcomes%2C%20which%20is%20not%20necessarily%20helpful%20in%20terms%20of%20that%20global%20growth.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Shah%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20bring%20India%20into%20the%20international%20fold%20even%20more.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20things%20that%20India%20could%20do%20to%20help%20unite%20and%20grow%20the%20game%2C%20including%20commercially%20helping%20to%20pool%20off-shore%20rights%2C%20using%20their%20teams%20to%20give%20opportunity%20to%20smaller%20full%20members%20and%20emerging%20countries%2C%20using%20their%20clout%20to%20open%20new%20territories%20and%20markets%2C%20collaborating%20closely%20with%20the%20ICC%20to%20help%20benefit%20members%2C%20as%20examples%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarclay%20admitted%20that%20presently%20there%20is%20an%20overkill%20of%20cricket%20and%20at%20times%20he%20even%20lost%20track%20of%20the%20congested%20international%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20reckon%2C%20gee%2C%20I'm%20at%20the%20apex%20of%20the%20game%20and%20I%20can't%20tell%20you%20who's%20playing%20around%20the%20world.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20didn't%20realise%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20were%20in%20South%20Africa%20until%20I%20read%20about%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Marco%20Jansen%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F113406-marco-jansen-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMarco%20Jansen%3C%2Fa%3E's%20seven%20wickets%20this%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20Barclay%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we've%20lost%20perspective.%20It's%20not%20great%20for%20the%20game%20at%20all.%20It's%20a%20mess.%20The%20calendar%20is%20incredibly%20congested%20and%20self-interest%20is%20such%20that%20it's%20almost%20impossible%20to%20untangle%20all%20of%20that%2C%20because%20no%20one's%20going%20to%20give%20up%20their%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarclay%20said%20ICC%20was%20right%20in%20not%20sanctioning%20Afghanistan's%20full%20membership%20membership%20status%20after%20the%20country's%20cricket%20Board%20was%20not%20allowed%20by%20the%20ruling%20Taliban%20government%20to%20field%20a%20women's%20team.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20the%20Afghanistan%20board's%20fault.%20They%20used%20to%20have%20women's%20cricket.%20I%20think%20our%20approach%20has%20been%20right.%20It%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20kick%20Afghanistan%20out%2C%20but%20their%20board%20haven't%20done%20anything%20wrong.%20They're%20just%20working%20under%20a%20decree%20and%20a%20series%20of%20laws%20that%20says%20this%20is%20what%20you%20have%20to%20do.%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20would%20make%20a%20jot%20of%20difference%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20there%20to%20kick%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20I'm%20a%20little%20na%C3%AFve%2C%20but%20I%20think%20cricket%20is%20such%20a%20force%20for%20good%20there%2C%20and%20it%20brings%20a%20lot%20of%20joy%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%20It%20is%20better%20to%20leave%20it%20there%20and%20hope%20that%20it%20can%20foster%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarclay%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20Cricket%20Australia%2C%20which%20cancelled%20multiple%20bilateral%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20but%20has%20played%20them%20in%20ICC%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20really%20want%20to%20make%20a%20political%20statement%2C%20don't%20play%20them%20in%20a%20World%20Cup.%20Sure%2C%20it%20might%20cost%20you%20a%20semifinal%20place%2C%20but%20principles%20are%20principles.%20It's%20not%20about%20having%20half%20a%20principle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733321640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F7842sbfo_jay-shah-afp_625x300_02_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fjay-shah-has-got-outgoing-icc-chairmans-honest-message-with-world-cricket-in-a-mess-7172169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Outgoing%20ICC%20chair%20Greg%20Barclay%20believes%20Jay%20Shah%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20pull%20cricket%20out%20of%20the%20current%20%26quot%3Bmess%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fjay-shah-has-got-outgoing-icc-chairmans-honest-message-with-world-cricket-in-a-mess-7172169%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Food%20inflation%20in%20policy%20formulation%20a%20complex%20issue%3A%20EAC-PM%20member%20Shah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733320731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Ffood-inflation-in-policy-formulation-a-complex-issue-eac-pm-member-shah-124120401086_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20July%2C%20Chief%20Economic%20Advisor%20V%20Anantha%20Nageswaran%20pitched%20for%20excluding%20food%20inflation%20from%20policy%20formulation%20which%20set%20it%20a%20fierce%20debate%20in%20policy%20circles%20with%20RBI%20resisting%20any%20such%20move%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jagan%20Reddy%20In%20Deep%20Waters%20In%20Row%20Over%20Port%20Shares%20Sale%2C%20Party%20Says%20%26quot%3BVendetta%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEx-Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Reddy%20and%20members%20of%20his%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20including%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Vijaysai%20Reddy%2C%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20illegally%20acquiring%2041.12%20per%20cent%20of%20shares%20in%20Kakinada%20Seaport%20Private%20Limited%20(KSPL)%2C%20and%2048.74%20per%20cent%20in%20Kakinada%20Special%20Export%20Zone%20(KSEZ)%2C%20for%20Rs%20500%20crore%20in%202020%2F21%2C%20when%20they%20were%20worth%20over%20Rs%203%2C600%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20First%20Information%20Report%2C%20or%20FIR%2C%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20YSRCP%20boss%20and%20his%20colleagues%20on%20basis%20of%20a%20complaint%20by%20Karnati%20Venkateswara%20Rao%2C%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Director%20of%20KSPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shares%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20were%20'bought'%20by%20the%20YSRCP%20leaders%20-%20and%20routed%20via%20a%20company%20called%20Aurobindo%20Realty%20(now%20Auro%20Infra)%20-%20through%20%26quot%3Bcheating%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20and%20conspiracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complainant%2C%20Y%20Vikranth%20Reddy%2C%20son%20of%20YSRCP%20leader%20YV%20Subba%20Reddy%2C%20had%20approached%20him%20%26quot%3Basking%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20part%20with%20his%20shares%20and%20claimed%20this%20was%20being%20demanded%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20then%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20if%20he%20did%20not%20agree%20to%20the%20transfer%20of%20shares%2C%20there%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bspate%20of%20criminal%20cases%20and%20vigilance%20enquiries%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest%20and%20that%20of%20his%20family%20members%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20also%20informed%20they%20will%20pay%20me%20a%20nominal%20amount%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20my%20shareholdings.%20All%20my%20efforts%20to%20convince%20them%20proved%20futile%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20alleged%20in%20the%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20also%20names%20Sarath%20Chandra%20Reddy%2C%20a%20non-executive%20director%20of%20Aurobindo%20Pharma%2C%20which%20filed%20a%20note%20with%20the%20BSE%20this%20morning%20distancing%20itself%2C%20and%20Auro%20Infra%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20from%20ownership%20of%2C%20or%20connection%20with%20operations%20of%2C%20Kakinada%20Seaports%20and%20Kakinada%20SEZ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20regard%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20clarify%20that%20(neither)%20Aurobindo%20Pharma%20Limited%20nor%20its%20subsidiaries%20are%20in%20any%20way%20connected%20with%20the%20ownership%20or%20operations%20of%20Kakinada%20Seaports%20Limited%20and%20Kakinada%20SEZ%20Limited%2C%20including%20Auro%20Infra%20Private%20Limited%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagan%20Reddy%20has%20not%20yet%20reacted%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20but%20senior%20YSRCP%20leader%20Kakani%20Govardhan%20Reddy%2C%20the%20former%20Food%20Processing%20Minister%2C%20refuted%20the%20allegations%20and%20claimed%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20vendetta%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20this%20is%20part%20of%20a%20political%20vendetta...%20part%20of%20a%20game%20being%20played%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20(whose%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20defeated%20the%20YSRCP%20in%20the%20May%20election).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20(Aurobindo%20Realty)%20wanted%20to%20acquire%20(the%20shares)%2C%20they%20could%20have%20acquired%20the%20entire%20stake%20and%20taken%20control%20of%20the%20port.%20Why%20only%20a%20partial%20stake%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20and%20also%20asked%20why%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20who%20continues%20to%20hold%20the%20majority%20stake%2C%20had%20waited%20nearly%20five%20years%20to%20make%20his%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20invited%20sharp%20attacks%20from%20the%20two%20main%20opposition%20parties%20-%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former's%20charge%20has%20been%20led%20by%20YS%20Sharmila%2C%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20estranged%20sister.%20Ms%20Sharmila%20has%20accused%20leaders%20of%20her%20brother's%20party%20of%20%26quot%3Bharassing%20the%20port%20owner%20to%20give%20up%20stake%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20deal%20is%20made%20for%2025%20years%2C%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20have%20to%20pay%20power%20bills%20that%20are%20hiked...%20the%20burden%20will%20fall%20on%20every%20family...%20they%20are%20going%20to%20pay%20lakhs%20of%20rupees%20because%20the%20government%20failed%20to%20do%20anything%20about%20this%20scam%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters%20outside%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20is%20demanding%20that%20at%20least%20the%20central%20government%20do%20something%20and%20scrap%20this%20deal.%20An%20inquiry%20should%20Be%20conducted%20and%20guilty%20must%20be%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20similar%20allegations%20involving%20the%20YSRCP%20and%20the%20Krishnapatnam%20and%20Gangavaram%20ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20CM%20Ramesh%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Andhra's%20Anakapelle%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20do%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20he%20threatened%20so%20many%20industries.%20Kakinada%20Port%20is%20just%20one%20of%20them...%20I%20know%20this%20story%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20He%20threatened%20them%2C%20saying%2C%20'If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20sit%20behind%20bars%20then%20you%20transfer%20the%20shares.'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20