Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20IndiGo%20said%20that%20India's%20aviation%20regulator%2C%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%2C%20publishes%20data%20on%20airline%20punctuality%20and%20customer%20complaints%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndiGo%20has%20consistently%20scored%20high%20on%20punctuality%20and%20has%20the%20lowest%20customer%20complaint%20ratio%20for%20an%20airline%20of%20its%20size%20and%20scale%20of%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20stated%20that%20the%20data%20published%20in%20the%20survey%20by%20AirHelp%2C%20an%20EU%20claim%20processing%20agency%2C%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20report%20the%20sample%20size%20from%20India%2C%20and%20neither%20takes%20into%20account%20the%20methodology%20or%20compensation%20guidelines%20used%20by%20the%20global%20aviation%20industry%20-%20casting%20a%20doubt%20on%20its%20credibility%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20India's%20most%20preferred%20airline%2C%20IndiGo%20refutes%20the%20findings%20of%20this%20survey%20and%20reiterates%20its%20promise%20of%20on-time%2C%20affordable%2C%20courteous%20and%20hassle-free%20travel%20experience%20for%20its%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20aviation%20major.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20DGCA%20data%2C%20during%20the%20nine-month%20period%20(January-September)%2C%20budget%20carrier%20IndiGo%20carried%20more%20than%207.25%20crore%20passengers%2C%20clocking%20a%20market%20share%20of%2061.3%20per%20cent%2C%20followed%20by%20Tata%20Group-run%20Air%20India%20flying%20over%201.64%20crore%20passengers%20with%2013.9%20per%20cent%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20fleet%20of%20more%20than%20380%20aircraft%2C%20the%20airline%20is%20operating%20around%202%2C100%20daily%20flights%20and%20connecting%20over%2085%20domestic%20destinations%20and%20more%20than%2030%20international%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrussels%20Airlines%2C%20Qatar%20Airways%20and%20United%20Airlines%20occupy