t%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20pitch.%20Under%20right%20conditions%2C%20right%20weather%2C%20the%20ball%20will%20move.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20morning%20of%20day%20three%2C%20no%20one%20would%20have%20expected%20that%20Test%20match%20to%20finish%20in%20three%20days.%20That%20was%20just%20really%20good%20bowling%20from%20Australia...I%20don't%20think%20the%20pitch%20played%20a%20part%20in%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20history%20of%20pink-ball%20Test%20cricket%20shows%20that%20batting%20during%20twilight%20poses%20the%20toughest%20challenges%20for%20batters.%20While%20Hough%20didn't%20have%20definitive%20information%2C%20he%20felt%20the%20common%20view%20of%20twilight%20sessions%20being%20tough%20for%20batters%20was%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20worry%20about%20the%20pitch%20preparation%20side%20of%20things%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20talk%20to%20the%20plaers%20in-depth%20about%20what%20they%20find%20challenging.%20But%20history%20suggests%20that%20the%20night%20time%20session%20tends%20to%20liven%20up%20a%20little%20bit%20in%20regards%20to%20if%20a%20new%20ball%2C%20or%20there's%20a%20declaration%20or%20they%20get%20them%20all%20out%20under%20lights%20in%20that%20last%20session%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20new%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20to%20then%20take%20a%20bit%20more%20to%20get%20used%20to.%20If%20you've%20got%20a%20couple%20of%20players%20in%2C%20they%20can%20navigate%20through%20that%20a%20lot%20easier.%20I%20know%20that%20they%20found%20it%20hard%20in%20the%20early%20days%20to%20pick%20the%20seam%20and%20even%20with%20the%20spinners.%20So%20I%20know%20Kookaburra%20have%20done%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20in%20with%20the%20ball%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20the%20finer%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20sort%20of%20just%20focus%20on%20my%20role%20within%20the%20game%20and%20preparing%20the%20pitch.%20I%20don't%20try%20to%20understand%20all%20of%20th