20trams%2C%20promotes%20cleaner%20and%20car-free%20travel%20options%20(Representational%20image)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20during%20times%20of%20high%20pollution%2C%20the%20city%20increases%20public%20transport%20services%20by%2010%25%20and%20offers%20discounted%20%E2%80%98T-aire%E2%80%99%20multi-ride%20tickets%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20use%20them.%20They%20also%20have%20schemes%20like%20the%20%E2%80%98T%20Verda%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20which%20offers%20a%20three-year%20free%20transit%20pass%20to%20people%20who%20scrap%20old%2C%20polluting%20vehicles%20and%20commit%20to%20not%20purchasing%20another%20%E2%80%94%20directly%20addressing%20emissions%20from%20private%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20air%20quality%20improves%20in%20the%20city%2C%20Barcelona%20is%20observing%20socio-economic%20benefits.%20There%20has%20been%20a%2030%25%20rise%20in%20commercial%20activity%2C%20especially%20in%20areas%20with%20reduced%20vehicle%20traffic%20and%20more%20pedestrian-friendly%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExpanding%20green%20spaces%20for%20cleaner%20air%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarcelona%20has%20also%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328522%2Fhow-nature-based-solutions-can-help-build-climate-change-resilience-wri-projects%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eurban%20greening%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20a%20goal%20of%20increasing%20its%20green%20spaces.%20They%20plan%20on%20adding%20more%20than%20160%20hectares%20of%20green%20space%20by%202030%2C%20which%20will%20help%20improve%20air%20quality%2C%20absorb%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20and%20manage%20the%20urban%20heat%20island%20effect.%20Green%20spaces%20like%20parks%2C%20gardens%2C%20and%20tree-lined%20streets%20provide%20a%20natural%20buffer%20to%20pollution.%20The%20%E2%80%9CTrees%20for%20Living%E2%80%9D%20initiative%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Ba