freely%20across%20the%20arid%20plains%20and%20open%20grasslands.%20Sadly%2C%20many%20of%20these%20animals%20have%20faced%20a%20drastic%20decline%20in%20numbers.%20The%20wolves%2C%20once%20abundant%20in%20the%20area%2C%20have%20vanished%20altogether%2C%20and%20the%20blackbuck%20is%20protected%20under%20the%20Wildlife%20Act%2C%201972%2C%20and%20listed%20as%20an%20extremely%20vulnerable%20species%20by%20PETA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIdentifying%20challenges%2C%20spreading%20awareness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20factor%20contributing%20to%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20wildlife%20crisis%20is%20the%20pollution%20of%20the%20Jojri%20River%2C%20which%20flows%20from%20Jodhpur%20to%20the%20south-west%20and%20stretches%20across%20the%20landscape%20for%20nearly%2083%20kilometres.%20The%20river%20is%20contaminated%20with%20chemical%20waste%20and%20untreated%20sewage%20from%20both%20industrial%20and%20domestic%20sources.%20This%20has%20created%20a%20dangerous%20situation%20for%20wildlife%2C%20particularly%20for%20animals%20that%20rely%20on%20the%20river%20for%20drinking%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20knew%20that%20the%20blackbucks%20were%20drinking%20the%20contaminated%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20tried%20to%20stop%20them%20by%20setting%20up%20some%20watering%20holes%2C%20but%20they%20still%20went%20back%20to%20the%20contaminated%20water%20because%20they%20had%20gotten%20used%20to%20drinking%20from%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%203298px)%20100vw%2C%203298px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223298%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bluckbuck%20drinking%20the%20polluted%20Jogri%20river's%20water.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809.jpeg%203298w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809-1536x1024.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809-2048x1366.jpeg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809-1200x800.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.51.19-PM_11zon-1732713809-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-383604%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222199%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Jojri%20river%20runs%20black.%20Left%20with%20few%20alternatives%2C%20the%20wildlife%20still%20depends%20on%20its%20water.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20became%20even%20more%20dire%20when%20feral%20dogs%2C%20now%20the%20only%20carnivores%20in%20the%20area%2C%20began%20attacking%20injured%20blackbucks.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20wildlife%20used%20to%20survive%20here%20because%20of%20the%20agricultural%20land%2C%20for%20both%20food%20and%20shelter%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20now%20those%20lands%20have%20barbed%20wire%20fences%20to%20protect%20the%20crops.%20These%20fences%20end%20up%20hurting%20the%20animals.%20The%20blackbucks%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20are%20often%20found%20stuck%20in%20the%20wires%2C%20injured%2C%20and%20because%20they%20are%20trapped%2C%20they%20are%20attacked%20by%20the%20feral%20dogs.%E2%80%9D%20This%20has%20led%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20injuries%20and%20deaths%2C%20further%20threatening%20the%20already%20vulnerable%20species.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20challenges%2C%20Sharvan%20and%20his%20team%20have%20started%20working%20on%20informing%20and%20sensitising%20people.%20Every%20time%20they%20get%20a%20call%20about%20an%20injured%20animal%2C%20they%20make%20sure%20to%20inform%20the%20people%20living%20in%20and%20around%20that%20part%20of%20the%20village.%20They%20show%20images%20and%20videos%20of%20animals%20that%20are%20harmed%20because%20of%20these%20wires%20to%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20farms.%20By%20letting%20them%20know%20the%20harsh%20consequences%20of%20their%20poorly%20thought-out%20actions%2C%20Sharvan%20makes%20sure%20to%20make%20them%20take%20responsibility.%20And%20it%20is%20but%20human%20nature%20to%20be%20considerate%20moving%20forth.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafeguarding%20the%20Orans%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20replenish%20the%20lands%2C%20their%20team%20has%20also%20uprooted%20invasive%20species%20of%20Julie%20flora%2C%20and%20planted%20native%20grasses%20to%20create%20grazing%20areas%20for%20the%20wildlife.%20They%20have%20focused%20on%20species%20like%20%3Cem%3Eber%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20Jujube)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekhejri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejaal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Pilu%20Tree)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekumatiya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Acacia%20Senegal)%2C%20which%20are%20native%20to%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CChinkaras%20and%20blackbucks%20love%20%3Cem%3Eber%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20lot%2C%20so%20we%20plant%20those%20every%20year%20to%20replant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F60652%2Ffighting-deforestation-oran-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lands%20of%20Oran%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrans%20%E2%80%94%20sacred%20groves%20that%20have%20traditionally%20been%20protected%20by%20rural%20communities%20%E2%80%94%20play%20a%20central%20role%20in%20Sharvan%E2%80%99s%20conservation%20efforts.%20These%20groves%20are%20rich%20in%20biodiversity%20and%20often%20include%20water%20bodies%20that%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20local%20wildlife.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Sharvan%E2%80%99s%20significant%20breakthroughs%20came%20when%20he%20and%20his%20team%20began%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20water%20ponds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ponds%20that%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20for%20the%20animals%20to%20drink%20from%20were%20being%20dug%20too%20deep%20for%20them%20to%20reach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20This%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20smaller%20animals%2C%20like%20rabbits%2C%20to%20access%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20inspiration%20from%20the%20shallow%20saucer-like%20ponds%20he%20had%20seen%20at%20Tal%20Chhapar%20Sanctuary%20in%20Nagaur%2C%20Sharvan%20and%20his%20team%2C%20with%20funding%20from%20Intact%20(Chapter%20Jodhpur)%20built%20shallow%20water%20ponds%20in%20the%20Orans%2C%20making%20them%20accessible%20to%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20wildlife.%20T